<%- layout('layouts/boilerplate') %> 

<h1 class="display-5 fw-bold"><%= library.name %></h1>
<p class="fs-5 fw-semibold text-muted"><%= library.location %></p>

<div>
    <div class="card my-3">
        <div class="row g-0">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            
            <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="true">
                <div class="carousel-indicators">
                  <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                  <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                  <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                  <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1e/Salle_de_lecture_Biblioth%C3%A8que_Mazarine_depuis_gallerie.jpg/1200px-Salle_de_lecture_Biblioth%C3%A8que_Mazarine_depuis_gallerie.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                  </div>
                  <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/72/NYC_-_New_York_City_Library_-_1723.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                  </div>
                  <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="https://www.readingkingdom.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/halpern_1-041819.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="prev">
                  <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                </button>
                <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide="next">
                  <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                  <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                </button>
              </div>

          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column" style="height:100%">
              <h5 class="card-title"><%= library.type %> Library</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Repellendus omnis ab debitis modi, saepe similique, ut obcaecati blanditiis tenetur qui ducimus eum consectetur beatae quae a autem praesentium sit vel.
              Et dolores sint rem maiores hic illum adipisci magnam minus. Dignissimos excepturi distinctio incidunt adipisci corrupti, et explicabo velit molestiae impedit mollitia, sequi sunt ad quis reprehenderit temporibus praesentium nemo.
              Corrupti tempore nisi neque dicta quasi harum blanditiis qui? Reprehenderit, in iusto beatae fugiat culpa eius totam illo vel error. Vel doloribus cumque ipsam rem accusantium nam excepturi a numquam.
              Quisquam blanditiis facere voluptates. At, pariatur! Rerum vero eos commodi doloremque excepturi voluptatum obcaecati fugiat ipsa corporis accusantium voluptatibus quam ipsum, eaque debitis, saepe iste voluptas fugit qui eligendi. Veniam.</p>
                <div class="ms-auto mt-auto">
                    <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Created on <%= createdAt %></small></p>
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
</div>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p><%= library.librarianAndStuff %></p>
<ul>
    <% for (let day of library.operatingDays) { %> 
        <li><%= day %> </li>
    <% } %> 
</ul>
<p><%= library.openTime %></p>
<p><%= library.closeTime %></p>
